data.description: Always want that little ranch  and a rural lifestyle still close to town ? This one is 4.15 acres with mobile home and fenced acreage and barn/run in. home has a metal roof and screened in porch along with handicap accessible ramps. over 1500 square ft of conditioned area and a total of 2186 sq ft everyone should have plenty of space.New flooring has been authorized for this one, waiting on install date. 3 beds and 2 baths, a family room with fireplace and separate living room allows you to spread out. This property has two RV hookups with water and electric. The carport also has an enclosed area in the rear for your tools. Several fenced corral areas and a practice area for barrel racing as well as a barn/run in for for your animals. A great little place to raise your family in rural Levy county, take a tour through Williston today it's growing!
